" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Fără configurare necesară</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Funcționalități mobile de bază incluse</span></div></div></div><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-primary/8 to-teal-primary/12 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-teal-primary/20 shadow-sm"><div class="text-center mb-6"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-teal-primary/20 text-teal-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-teal-primary/30">Supliment Opțional</span></div></div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Aplicație White-Label</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-center mb-6">Publicați sub marca proprie cu integrări extinse de dispozitive și control complet asupra brandingului.</p><div class="space-y-3"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Branding-ul cabinetului dvs.</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class